{
  "name": "OLEDBError",
  "summary": "<p><strong>OLEDBError</strong> 对象是 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/OLEDBErrors/OLEDBErrors .htm#OLEDBErrors.OLEDBErrors\">OLEDBErrors</a></strong> 集合的成员。如果指定的 OLE DB 查询运行时没有出现错误，则 <strong>OLEDBErrors</strong> 集合为空。集合中错误的索引次序与 OLE DB 提供程序生成它们时的次序相同。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Application/Application .htm#Application.ODBCErrors\">OLEDBErrors</a></strong>( <em>index</em> )（其中 <em>index</em> 是 OLE DB 错误的索引号）可返回一个 <strong>OLEDBError</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示最近的 OLEDB 查询返回的第一个错误的错误说明以及SqlState属性的值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> error = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">OLEDBErrors</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`The following error occurred:<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${error.ErrorString}</span> : <span class=\"hljs-subst\">${error.SqlState}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一个 OLEDB 错误的字符串赋值给 A7 单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A7&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">OLEDBErrors</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ErrorString</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表由上一次 OLE DB 查询所返回的 OLE DB 错误。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "ErrorString",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>String</strong> 值，它代表 OLEDB 错误字符串。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一个 OLEDB 错误的字符串。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">OLEDBErrors</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ErrorString</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一个 OLEDB 错误的字符串赋值给 I1 单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">OLEDBErrors</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ErrorString</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Number",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回用于指定错误号的数值。该错误号对应于某个唯一的陷阱，而该陷阱又对应于最近一次 OLE DB 查询所产生的错误条件。<strong>Long</strong> 类型，只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示最近一次 OLEDB 查询返回的本地错误号和其他错误信息。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> error = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">OLEDBErrors</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`The following error occurred: <span class=\"hljs-subst\">${error.<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Number</span>}</span>,<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${error.ErrorString}</span>:<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${error.SqlState}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一个 OLEDB 错误的错误号。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">OLEDBErrors</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Number</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "SqlState",
      "summary": "<p>有关特定错误的解释，请参阅 SQL 文档。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回 SQL 状态错误。<strong>String</strong> 型，只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一个 OLEDB 错误的 SQL 状态错误。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">OLEDBErrors</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SqlState</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一个 OLEDB 错误的 SQL 状态错误赋值给 I1 单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">OLEDBErrors</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SqlState</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Stage",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个数字值，此值指定最近一次 OLE DB 查询所产生的错误的阶段。<strong>Long</strong> 类型，只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示由最近一次 OLEDB 查询所返回的错误号、阶段以及其他错误信息。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> error = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">OLEDBErrors</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`The following error occurred: <span class=\"hljs-subst\">${error.<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Number</span>}</span>,<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${error.Stage}</span>,<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${error.ErrorString}</span>:<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${error.SqlState}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一个 OLEDB 错误产生的阶段。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">OLEDBErrors</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Stage</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": []
}